<p><em>For posterity, the original guide is below.</em></p>
<h1 id='how-to-participate-in-a-raindance'>How to Participate in a Raindance</h1>
<p>This guide will walk you through the process.</p>

<p>Here&#39;s a quick screen recording of a raindance taking place:<br>
<a href="https://vimeo.com/258816694">TurtleCoin - Participating in Raindance on Vimeo</a></p>
<h2 id='raindance'>raindance</h2>
<p><img src="/guides/images/raindance/rain1.jpg" alt="Raindance Channel" /></p>

<p>A raindance happens when the TurtleBotRain wallet has accumulated 5,000 or more TRTL.</p>

<p><img src="/guides/images/raindance/forecast.jpg" alt="Forecast" /></p>

<p>When TurtleBotRain posts in the #raindance channel, it means a raindance is about to begin!</p>

<p><img src="/guides/images/raindance/tuttut.jpg" alt="A Raindance is about to begin" /></p>

<p>When you see this message the raindance will begin soon.
Get your TRTL wallet address ready.</p>

<p><strong>Wait</strong> and especially <strong>don&#39;t click on any reactions or emotes yet. This will cause a disqualification!</strong></p>

<p>Wait for the “Quick, send me your wallet addresses!” message.</p>

<p><img src="/guides/images/raindance/quick_rain.jpg" alt="Quick, send your wallet!" /></p>

<p>Click on TurtleBotRain to send your address in a private message to it.</p>

<p><img src="/guides/images/raindance/turtlebotrain.jpg" alt="Click on this" /></p>

<p><img src="/guides/images/raindance/pm_bot.jpg" alt="DM the bot" /></p>

<p>You should receive a private message back that will look like something like this:</p>

<p><img src="/guides/images/raindance/respo1.jpg" alt="You get a response" /></p>

<p>or</p>

<p><img src="/guides/images/raindance/respo2.jpg" alt="You get a different resopnse" /></p>

<p><strong>The Emoji will be different for everyone</strong></p>

<p>Now return to the #raindance channel and react with the emoji you received in the private message.</p>

<p><img src="/guides/images/raindance/react.jpg" alt="React" /></p>

<p>Only click the emoji listed in the private message.</p>

<p>If you did everything correctly you will be included in the payout! Congrats!
TurtleBotRain will reply with the amount that you&#39;ll receive.</p>

<p><img src="/guides/images/raindance/payout.jpg" alt="Payout!" /></p>
<h2 id='rain'>!rain</h2>
<p><img src="/guides/images/raindance/forecast.jpg" alt="Forecast" /></p>

<p>If you type <code>!rain</code> <strong>in the bots channel only</strong> you should get a response back with how many turtles are needed for the next raindance.</p>
<h2 id='notify'>Notify</h2>
<p><img src="/guides/images/raindance/notify.jpg" alt="Notification" /></p>

<p>Enabling notifications for the #raindance channel is easy.</p>

<p>Click the dropdown arrow.</p>

<p><img src="/guides/images/raindance/notify1.jpg" alt="Dropdown" /></p>

<p>Click on notification settings.</p>

<p><img src="/guides/images/raindance/notify2.jpg" alt="Notification Settings" /></p>

<p>Scroll down.</p>

<p><img src="/guides/images/raindance/notify3.jpg" alt="Scroll on down" /></p>

<p>Look for notification overrides.</p>

<p><img src="/guides/images/raindance/notify4.jpg" alt="Notifcation Overrides" /></p>

<p>Select &quot;raindance&quot;.</p>

<p><img src="/guides/images/raindance/notify5.jpg" alt="Select Raindance" /></p>

<p>Select &quot;All&quot;.</p>

<p><img src="/guides/images/raindance/notify6.jpg" alt="Select All" /></p>

<p>Done.</p>

<p><strong>Note: If notifications don&#39;t work, follow these steps-</strong></p>

<ol>
<li><p>Go to <code>User Settings</code> (the little gear icon to the right of your name in the bottom left)</p></li>
<li><p>Click on <code>Notifications</code></p></li>
<li><p>Enable <code>Enable Desktop Notifications</code></p></li>
</ol>

<p><img src="/guides/images/raindance/notif.png" alt="desktopnotify" /></p>
